sellerCard.oneLiner: Self Taught Web Designer and Developer
sellerCard.description: Hey! My name is Megan. I am a Self taught and driven individual dedicated to meeting your digital needs. I have completed over 200+ freelancing projects. I have expertise in designing and developing e-commerce platforms in Squarespace and Shopify. I am also a circle member of Squarespace!

description.content:
Let's chat before booking to ensure we are on the same page!


Need a custom page amount website? Message me today for a custom quote.


Hi! My name is Meg, I'm from Arizona and am a full-time web designer on Fiverr. I am also a Squarespace circle member and completed the StandOut Squarespace Program.


  • I am an experienced designer as well as a developer.
  • I have extensive experience in e-commerce and online stores.
  • I'm here to assist you with bringing your vision to life.
  • I will build a Squarespace website designed for your business needs.
  • I will customize your site to your branding.


I am excited to make your business come to life!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What version of Squarespace do you work on?
Do you do branding kits?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do offer full branding & logo design please message me and we can discuss!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of websites do you build?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I can build almost any kind of website!
Portfolios, Ecommerce, Blogs, Business, you name it!
Send me a message and we can discuss.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I already have a website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You are more than welcome to send me your store URL and use my Review gig or my redesign services. Contact me for a custom offer for your web redesign.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if my domain is hosted by somewhere other then squarespace?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Thats perfectly fine! We can connect it or transfer it!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide web maintenance and support services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I help with ongoing maintenance services to your store ( I can do schedule uploading of content, design your store according to relevant holidays, sale days, etc) and I can also help you with social media as well!

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do I provide you information on products or content for my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can send files through our chat here, or, if it;s to large to send – we can use google drive / one drive.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work on Shopify?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I currently am not accepting new clients for Shopify.

reviews.comment: Meg is exceptional! I am for better or worse, a branding stickler. I have worked with luxury brands like Audi, the BBC and Lululemon previously and as a result of that, have high standards for design and UX. She picked up my brand and needs without missing a beat and found ways to elevate my request, not to mention she was so incredibly quick to deliver my project. It was so seamless working with Meg and I’d trust her to take charge on any deign or web based project. She took my vague vision and turned into something sharp, elegant and valuable - what a dream! I feel so lucky to have found Meg and appreciate how seamless and easy working with her was. If only every creative project wow’d me like this!
Meg took what I had in my head and created a beautiful website - often with little direction. She is my go-to as we continue to expand out business. Her instinct for decision and U/I were spot on.

Meg delivered an OUTSTANDING website that truly exceeded expectations! Her politeness, timely delivery, and proactive communication made the collaboration seamless. Highly recommend working with her! 👏
Thank you for your help again!
Meg is amazing. Very professional, makes great suggestions & delivers quality work every time. Thank you so much Meg!
